{"tid":2223962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貝多芬《歡樂頌》變禁歌？ 內地網傳「新教師紀律」","createTime":"2020-09-30T07:51:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T13:08:19.000Z","uid":271829,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9b00a502fa1735f59656b7f593cb25641c2bfce3","tid":2223962,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T07:51:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rZfAJy_Y58BrmN_3DQI_MqtlRCc=/1200x675/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6M6QQNJU7JH4RAC54A3YV2ZELM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrZfAJy_Y58BrmN_3DQI_MqtlRCc%3D%2F1200x675%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6M6QQNJU7JH4RAC54A3YV2ZELM.jpg&h=d2317204&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網傳內地新教師紀律將貝多芬的《歡樂頌》列為宗教禁歌。(路透社)<br />\n...<br />\n中共打壓宗教，內地社交媒體流傳新學期的「教師紀律」中，當局竟將著名音樂家貝多芬的第九號交響曲第四樂章（Beethoven Symphony No. 9），即俗稱的《歡樂頌》定為「宗教音樂」，不可用作教材，消息引發內地網民議論。<br />\n相關消息分別在豆瓣及新浪微博流傳，有指新學期的教師紀律中，「領導指示，為了全面貫徹國家對教育工作的要求，我們要規避宗教音樂在教材中出現，包括有宗教背景的樂器音樂」，並請教師自行調整教材，一旦出現「問題」就要負責，被禁的曲目包括《歡樂頌》。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200930/5TPEJPACYREI5CFQNA36GXQ74A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200930%2F5TPEJPACYREI5CFQNA36GXQ74A%2F&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWLe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=4a00c292\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200930%2F5TPEJPACYREI5CFQNA36GXQ74A%2F&h=14e15452\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200930/5TPEJPACYREI5CFQNA36GXQ74A/</a>"},{"pid":"bbe35b46cd0184143277ba4da445a2ada77c6b92","tid":2223962,"uid":375425,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T07:58:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"295dc2276c4fd86f4eb9fe603d7e6d0e84cc2f3a","tid":2223962,"uid":136416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-